paragraphs.text: %jdbc CREATE PARTITION FUNCTION PF_TS(TS TIMESTAMP) AS RANGE BOUNDARIES(TIMESTAMP '2017-01-20 00:00:00', TIMESTAMP '2017-02-10 00:00:00') USING com.sap.spark.engines
%jdbc CREATE PARTITION SCHEME PS_TS USING PF_TS USING com.sap.spark.engines

%jdbc CREATE TABLE SENSOR_DATA ( TEMP int, HUM int, TS TIMESTAMP )
SERIES ( PERIOD FOR SERIES TS 
START TIMESTAMP '2017-01-01 00:00:00' 
END TIMESTAMP '2017-02-27 23:59:00')
PARTITION BY PS_TS( TS )
USING com.sap.spark.engines
OPTIONS (
files "/user/vora/sensor.csv"
,csvskip "1"
,storagebackend "hdfs")
%jdbc ``SELECT median(HUM) from SENSOR_DATA WHERE PERIOD AS OF TIMESTAMP '2017-01-01 00:00:00'`` USING com.sap.spark.engines

%jdbc
``SELECT * FROM GRANULIZE
( SERIES SENSOR_DATA, 1 DAY, EVEN => DESCRIPTOR(TEMP,HUM) ) G`` USING com.sap.spark.engines
